name: Emmett
content:
Emmett was a Human male smuggler fence who operated near the Imperial Outpost on the planet Lok during the time of the Galactic Civil War. During this time, he resided in a small tent some distance away from the Galactic Empire's installation.
Emmett was a non-player character in the 2003 video game Star Wars Galaxies, a massively multiplayer online roleplaying game developed by Sony Online Entertainment and published by LucasArts, prior to its closure on December 15, 2011. Emmett was added to the game along with the smuggling missions introduced with the "Chapter 3" update, released on September 27, 2006.
